co.cask.coopr.http.handler

Class ProvisionerHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.http.AbstractHttpHandler
      • co.cask.coopr.http.handler.AbstractAuthHandler
        • co.cask.coopr.http.handler.ProvisionerHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    co.cask.http.HttpHandler

    @Path(value="/v2")
public final class ProvisionerHandler
extends AbstractAuthHandler
    Handles requests from provisioners to register themselves, send heartbeats, delete themselves, and get plugin resources.
